{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"There's an old saying, \"Just because you can't see something,"},{"time":3000,"text":"doesn't mean it's not there.\""},{"time":6000,"text":"My work is -- it's a reflection of myself."},{"time":13000,"text":"What I wanted to do is to"},{"time":17000,"text":"show the world that the little things"},{"time":22000,"text":"can be the biggest things."},{"time":25000,"text":"We all seem to think that,"},{"time":28000,"text":"you know, if we look down on the ground, there's nothing there."},{"time":34000,"text":"And we use the word \"nothing.\""},{"time":37000,"text":"Nothing doesn't exist, because there is always something."},{"time":40000,"text":"My mother told me that, when I was a child,"},{"time":42000,"text":"that I should always respect the little things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47000,"text":"What made me do this work? I shall go into my story."},{"time":51000,"text":"This all started when I was age five."},{"time":55000,"text":"What made me do it? At school, I will admit this:"},{"time":58000,"text":"academically, I couldn't express myself."},{"time":61000,"text":"So I was, more or less, classed as \"nothing.\""},{"time":66000,"text":"My world was seen as less."},{"time":71000,"text":"So I decided I didn't really want to be a part of that world."},{"time":75000,"text":"I thought, I need to retreat"},{"time":79000,"text":"into something else."},{"time":81000,"text":"So when my mother used to take me to school,"},{"time":84000,"text":"she thought I was at school,"},{"time":86000,"text":"and I used to do a U-turn, when her back was turned,"},{"time":89000,"text":"and run off and hide in the shed at the back of the garden."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93000,"text":"Now, the one time I was in the shed,"},{"time":98000,"text":"and my mother suspected something,"},{"time":101000,"text":"thinking I was at school."},{"time":103000,"text":"My mother was like the woman in Tom and Jerry."},{"time":107000,"text":"So you'd just see her feet."},{"time":110000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":114000,"text":"So I was hiding in the shed, like that."},{"time":118000,"text":"And all of a sudden ..."},{"time":123000,"text":"And then I saw her legs."},{"time":127000,"text":"And then she said -- grabbed me like that, because my mother was quite big --"},{"time":130000,"text":"and she lifted me up and she says,"},{"time":133000,"text":"\"How come you're not at school?\""},{"time":135000,"text":"I told her I couldn't face it because the way"},{"time":138000,"text":"the teacher was treating me, ridiculing me,"},{"time":141000,"text":"and using me as an example of failure."},{"time":144000,"text":"So I told her."},{"time":146000,"text":"At that age, obviously, I couldn't express it that way,"},{"time":150000,"text":"but I told her I didn't feel right."},{"time":153000,"text":"And then she just said, \"You're going back to school tomorrow.\""},{"time":155000,"text":"And walked off. And I didn't expect that,"},{"time":157000,"text":"because I expected one of these ..."},{"time":161000,"text":"But I didn't get it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163000,"text":"So I'm sitting there thinking."},{"time":165000,"text":"And as I looked down on the ground,"},{"time":169000,"text":"I noticed there was some ants running around."},{"time":173000,"text":"And I went into this little fantasy world."},{"time":175000,"text":"And I thought,"},{"time":177000,"text":"\"These ants, are they looking for the queen ant?"},{"time":182000,"text":"Or do they need somewhere to live?\""},{"time":184000,"text":"So I thought \"Perhaps,"},{"time":186000,"text":"if I made these ants some apartments,"},{"time":190000,"text":"they'll move in.\""},{"time":194000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":198000,"text":"So I did."},{"time":200000,"text":"And how I set about that, I got some splinters of wood."},{"time":203000,"text":"And I sliced the little splinters of wood with a broken shard of glass,"},{"time":206000,"text":"constructed this little apartment."},{"time":210000,"text":"Well it looked like a little shanty shed when I'd finished."},{"time":215000,"text":"But I thought, perhaps the ant won't know, it'll probably move in."},{"time":217000,"text":"And so they did."},{"time":219000,"text":"That was a bit crude, at the time. And I made all these little apartments"},{"time":222000,"text":"and little merry-go-rounds, seesaws and swings, little ladders."},{"time":226000,"text":"And then I encouraged the ants to come 'round by putting sugar and things like that."},{"time":230000,"text":"And then I sat down and all the ants came along."},{"time":236000,"text":"And all I could hear was \"Is this for us?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":239000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":241000,"text":"And I say, \"Yes, they're all for you.\""},{"time":243000,"text":"And they moved in, and decided not to pay me any rent."},{"time":247000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":250000,"text":"And from there I was watching this little world."},{"time":253000,"text":"It became part of me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258000,"text":"When I discovered that I had this gift,"},{"time":265000,"text":"I wanted to experiment with this world"},{"time":269000,"text":"that we can't see."},{"time":271000,"text":"So I realized that there was more to life"},{"time":274000,"text":"than just everything that we see around us that's huge."},{"time":278000,"text":"So I started to educate myself on this molecular level."},{"time":283000,"text":"And as I got older, I continued. I showed my mother."},{"time":287000,"text":"My mother told me to take it smaller."}]},{"cues":[{"time":289000,"text":"Now I shall show you something here."},{"time":293000,"text":"And I'll explain."},{"time":296000,"text":"As you can see,"},{"time":299000,"text":"that's a pinhead."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":305000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":313000,"text":"Now that is called the Huf Haus."},{"time":317000,"text":"The gentleman who commissioned me to do this"},{"time":319000,"text":"was a gentleman called Peter Huf."},{"time":322000,"text":"And he says to me \"Willard, can you put my house on a pinhead?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":326000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":331000,"text":"So I say, \"How are you going to fit in there?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":334000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":337000,"text":"And then he said to me,"},{"time":340000,"text":"\"I don't believe you can do it. Can you really do it?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":343000,"text":"And I says, \"Well, try me.\""},{"time":347000,"text":"And then he said, \"But I don't believe that you can do this.\" So I said, \"OK.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":353000,"text":"So, to cut a long story short,"},{"time":355000,"text":"I went home, went underneath the microscope,"},{"time":357000,"text":"and I crushed up a piece of glass,"},{"time":361000,"text":"crushed it up."},{"time":363000,"text":"And underneath the microscope"},{"time":365000,"text":"there were splinters of glass."},{"time":367000,"text":"Some of them were quite jagged."},{"time":370000,"text":"So I was crushing up these pieces of glass,"},{"time":372000,"text":"which, as you can see,"},{"time":375000,"text":"that's the actual frame of the house."},{"time":377000,"text":"And the actual roof is made up of a fiber,"},{"time":383000,"text":"which I found in my sister's old teddy bear."},{"time":386000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":389000,"text":"So I got the teddy bear and I said,"},{"time":391000,"text":"\"Do you mind if I pull out one of your fibers?\""},{"time":394000,"text":"So I did."},{"time":396000,"text":"And I looked at it beneath the microscope. And some of it was flat."},{"time":399000,"text":"So I decided to slice these up"},{"time":401000,"text":"with the tool that I make"},{"time":403000,"text":"by -- I sharpen the end of a needle into a blade."},{"time":407000,"text":"And then I actually"},{"time":409000,"text":"slow down my whole nervous system."},{"time":412000,"text":"And then I work between my heartbeat,"},{"time":415000,"text":"I have one-and-a-half seconds"},{"time":418000,"text":"to actually move."},{"time":420000,"text":"And at the same time I have to watch I don't inhale"},{"time":422000,"text":"my own work, at the same time."},{"time":424000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":427000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":433000,"text":"Because that has happened to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":439000,"text":"So what I did, like I said, come back to the glass."},{"time":442000,"text":"I found these little bits of glass."},{"time":444000,"text":"And I had to make them square."},{"time":447000,"text":"So I'm thinking \"How can I do this?\""},{"time":449000,"text":"So what I did, I got an oilstone. Broke the edge of an oilstone off."},{"time":453000,"text":"And what I did, I took pieces of glass. And I started to rub them."},{"time":457000,"text":"I used a little tweezer which I made from a hair clip."},{"time":460000,"text":"And I built rubber around the end of the tweezer so it wouldn't crush the glass."},{"time":464000,"text":"And then I started rubbing, very very gently,"},{"time":469000,"text":"till some of the edges were quite square. And then I constructed it."},{"time":473000,"text":"And how I constructed it,"},{"time":475000,"text":"is by making grooves in the top of the pinhead."},{"time":478000,"text":"And then pushing the glass in with its own friction."},{"time":481000,"text":"And as I was doing it, what happened?"},{"time":484000,"text":"The instrument that I used turned into a catapult."},{"time":488000,"text":"And it went like this ..."},{"time":492000,"text":"And then that was it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":495000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":496000,"text":"Gone."},{"time":498000,"text":"So I'm thinking, \"Mr. Huf isn't going to be very happy"},{"time":500000,"text":"when I told him his house has gone to another,"},{"time":503000,"text":"into the atmosphere somewhere.\""},{"time":506000,"text":"So to cut the story short,"},{"time":508000,"text":"I decided that I had to go back and do it."},{"time":510000,"text":"So I found some more. And I decided to, sort of,"},{"time":513000,"text":"construct it very, very slowly,"},{"time":515000,"text":"holding my breath, working between my heartbeat,"},{"time":518000,"text":"and making sure everything is leveled."},{"time":520000,"text":"Because it's such a small sculpture,"},{"time":524000,"text":"nothing can go wrong."},{"time":526000,"text":"And I decided to build it up."},{"time":529000,"text":"Then I used fibers out of my jumper,"},{"time":532000,"text":"which I held and stretched."},{"time":534000,"text":"And made the beams going around the house."},{"time":536000,"text":"And the actual windows and the balcony"},{"time":538000,"text":"had to be sort of constructed."},{"time":540000,"text":"I used a money spider's web"},{"time":542000,"text":"to actually attach certain things,"},{"time":544000,"text":"which sent me insane."},{"time":546000,"text":"But I managed to do it."},{"time":549000,"text":"And when I finished it, I came back the next day."},{"time":552000,"text":"I noticed that the house was occupied."},{"time":556000,"text":"Have we ever heard of a dust mite?"},{"time":560000,"text":"Darren dust mite and his family moved in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":562000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":565000,"text":"So basically I'd completed the house."},{"time":569000,"text":"And there you are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":572000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":579000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":583000,"text":"Right. As you can see,"},{"time":585000,"text":"Bart Simpson is having a little argument."},{"time":589000,"text":"I think they're arguing about the space on the pin."},{"time":592000,"text":"There's not enough room for the two of them."},{"time":595000,"text":"So I didn't think he was going to throw Bart off."},{"time":597000,"text":"I think he was just warning him actually."},{"time":599000,"text":"But this one was made out of a nylon tag"},{"time":603000,"text":"out of my shirt."},{"time":605000,"text":"What I did, I plucked the tag out"},{"time":608000,"text":"and put it underneath the microscope."},{"time":611000,"text":"I used the needle which has got a slight blade on the end."},{"time":614000,"text":"Can anybody see the blade on the end of that needle?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":616000,"text":"Audience: No."}]},{"cues":[{"time":618000,"text":"WW: So what I did is the same process where I"},{"time":621000,"text":"just kind of hold my breath"},{"time":624000,"text":"and just work away very, very slowly,"},{"time":628000,"text":"manipulating the plastic, cutting it, because it behaves different."},{"time":632000,"text":"Whenever you work on that level, things behave different."},{"time":635000,"text":"Because it's on this molecular level things change"},{"time":637000,"text":"and they act different."},{"time":639000,"text":"And sometimes they turn into little catapults and things go up in the air."},{"time":642000,"text":"And, you know, all different things happen."},{"time":645000,"text":"But I had to make a little barrier, going around it, out of cellophane,"},{"time":648000,"text":"to stop it moving."},{"time":650000,"text":"Then static electricity set in."},{"time":652000,"text":"And it went ..."},{"time":654000,"text":"And I'm trying to remove it. And the static is interfering with everything."},{"time":657000,"text":"So there is sweat dripping off my head,"},{"time":660000,"text":"because I have to carve Homer Simpson like that, in that position."},{"time":665000,"text":"And after I've cut out the shape,"},{"time":667000,"text":"then I have to make sure that there is room for Bart's neck."}]},{"cues":[{"time":671000,"text":"So after I've done the same thing,"},{"time":673000,"text":"then I have to paint it."},{"time":675000,"text":"And after I've actually sculpted them,"},{"time":677000,"text":"I have to paint them."},{"time":679000,"text":"I experimented with a --"},{"time":682000,"text":"I found a dead fly."},{"time":684000,"text":"And I plucked the hair off the fly's head."},{"time":686000,"text":"Decided to make a paintbrush."},{"time":688000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":694000,"text":"But I would never do it to a living fly."},{"time":698000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":701000,"text":"Because I've heard a fly in pain."},{"time":706000,"text":"And they go \"Meow! Ow!\""},{"time":709000,"text":"Even though they get on our nerves,"},{"time":711000,"text":"I would never kill an insect"},{"time":713000,"text":"because, \"All creatures great and small\" --"},{"time":717000,"text":"there is a hymn that says that."},{"time":719000,"text":"So what I decided to do"},{"time":722000,"text":"is to pluck fine hair out of my face."},{"time":726000,"text":"And I looked at it underneath the microscope."},{"time":730000,"text":"That was the paintbrush."},{"time":732000,"text":"And whilst I'm painting I have to be very careful,"},{"time":734000,"text":"because the paint starts to turn into little blobs."},{"time":737000,"text":"And it starts to dry very quickly."},{"time":741000,"text":"So I have to be very quick."},{"time":744000,"text":"If I'm not, it will end up looking"},{"time":747000,"text":"not like what it's supposed to look like."},{"time":749000,"text":"It could end up looking like Humpty Dumpty or somebody else."},{"time":754000,"text":"So I have to be very very careful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":756000,"text":"This one took me approximately,"},{"time":760000,"text":"I would say, six to seven weeks."},{"time":763000,"text":"My work, rough estimate,"},{"time":765000,"text":"sometimes five, six to seven weeks;"},{"time":768000,"text":"you can't always anticipate."},{"time":772000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":779000,"text":"As you can see,"},{"time":781000,"text":"that's Charlton Heston brought down to size."},{"time":783000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":790000,"text":"He says to me, \"Willard\" --"},{"time":792000,"text":"You can see him saying, \"Why me?\""},{"time":796000,"text":"I says, \"I enjoyed your film. That's why.\""},{"time":798000,"text":"As you can see, there's an aphid fly there."},{"time":802000,"text":"That's just to show the scale"},{"time":804000,"text":"and the actual size of the sculpture."},{"time":807000,"text":"I would say it probably measures ..."},{"time":812000,"text":"a quarter of a millimeter."},{"time":814000,"text":"In America they say a period stop."},{"time":816000,"text":"So say if you cut a period stop in half,"},{"time":819000,"text":"a full stop, that's about the size of the whole thing."},{"time":823000,"text":"It's made -- the chariot is made of gold."}]},{"cues":[{"time":827000,"text":"And Charlton Heston is made of a floating fiber,"},{"time":831000,"text":"which I took out of the air."},{"time":833000,"text":"When the sunlight comes through the window you see these little fibers."},{"time":836000,"text":"And what I normally do is walk 'round a room --"},{"time":839000,"text":"(Laughter) --"},{"time":843000,"text":"trying to find one. And then I put it underneath the microscope."},{"time":846000,"text":"I remember one time I was doing it, and the window was open."},{"time":849000,"text":"And there was a lady standing by the bus stop."},{"time":851000,"text":"And she saw me walking around like this."},{"time":853000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":856000,"text":"And then she looked at me."},{"time":858000,"text":"And then I went ..."},{"time":863000,"text":"And then she went, \"Hmm, OK, he's not mad.\""},{"time":866000,"text":"Yeah, to actually do this thing --"},{"time":869000,"text":"the actual chariot is made of gold."},{"time":872000,"text":"I had a 24-karat gold ring."},{"time":874000,"text":"And I cut off a little flake of gold."},{"time":876000,"text":"And I bent it 'round,"},{"time":878000,"text":"and made it into the chariot."},{"time":880000,"text":"And the horse is made from nylon."},{"time":882000,"text":"And the spider's web is for the reins on the horse."},{"time":885000,"text":"To get the symmetrical shape of the horse"},{"time":887000,"text":"was very difficult,"},{"time":889000,"text":"because I had to get the horse to rear up"},{"time":891000,"text":"and look as though it was in some kind of action."}]},{"cues":[{"time":893000,"text":"When I did this one,"},{"time":895000,"text":"a gentleman seen it and said to me,"},{"time":897000,"text":"\"There's no way you can do this, you must have used some kind of machine."},{"time":900000,"text":"There's no way a man can do that."},{"time":902000,"text":"It must be a machine.\""},{"time":904000,"text":"So I says, \"OK then, if you say it's a machine ...\""},{"time":908000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":914000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":920000,"text":"That one took me approximately six weeks."},{"time":928000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":934000,"text":"The most famous statue in the world."},{"time":937000,"text":"This one, I would say,"},{"time":939000,"text":"was a serious challenge."},{"time":942000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":953000,"text":"Because I had to put the torch on the top."},{"time":956000,"text":"That one is, more or less, the same type of process."},{"time":960000,"text":"The bottom of it is carved from a grain of sand,"},{"time":966000,"text":"because I wanted to get a bit of the stone effect."},{"time":968000,"text":"I used a microscopic shard of diamond"},{"time":971000,"text":"to actually carve the actual base."},{"time":973000,"text":"Well, I can look at this one and I can be very proud of this,"},{"time":977000,"text":"because that statue has always sort of"},{"time":979000,"text":"kept an image in my head of, you know,"},{"time":981000,"text":"the beginning of people coming to America."},{"time":985000,"text":"So it's sort of Ellis Island, and seeing America for the first time."},{"time":989000,"text":"And that's the first thing they saw."},{"time":991000,"text":"So I wanted to have that little image."},{"time":993000,"text":"And this is it."},{"time":998000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1005000,"text":"And we all know that is the Hulk."},{"time":1008000,"text":"I wanted to create movement in the eye of a needle."},{"time":1011000,"text":"Because we know we see needles,"},{"time":1013000,"text":"but people aren't familiar with the eye of a needle"},{"time":1015000,"text":"apart from putting a thread through it."},{"time":1017000,"text":"So I broke the needle."},{"time":1019000,"text":"And made a needle look like"},{"time":1022000,"text":"the Hulk's broken it."},{"time":1024000,"text":"It's -- I had to make little holes"},{"time":1025000,"text":"in the base of the needle, to shove his feet in."},{"time":1027000,"text":"So most of my work, I don't use glue."},{"time":1030000,"text":"They go in with their own friction."},{"time":1032000,"text":"And that's how I managed to do it."},{"time":1034000,"text":"As you can see, he's looking at the moment. He's got a little grimace on his face."},{"time":1036000,"text":"And his mouth must be probably about"},{"time":1040000,"text":"three microns."},{"time":1043000,"text":"So the eyes are probably about one micron or something."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1049000,"text":"That ship there,"},{"time":1053000,"text":"that's made from 24-karat gold."},{"time":1055000,"text":"And I normally rig it with the web of a money spider."},{"time":1059000,"text":"But I had to rig it with strands of glue."},{"time":1062000,"text":"Because the web of the spider, it was sending me insane,"},{"time":1065000,"text":"because I couldn't get the web to move off."},{"time":1068000,"text":"And that's 24-karat gold. And it's constructed. I built it."},{"time":1071000,"text":"Constructed each plank of gold."},{"time":1075000,"text":"And the whole thing is sort of symmetrical."},{"time":1078000,"text":"The flag had to be made out of little strands of gold."},{"time":1081000,"text":"It's almost like doing a surgical operation to get this thing right."},{"time":1089000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1095000,"text":"As you can see, dressage."},{"time":1099000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":1101000,"text":"It's something I wanted to do just to show how I could get the symmetrical shape."},{"time":1104000,"text":"The actual rigging on the reins on the horse"},{"time":1107000,"text":"are made from the same sort of thing."},{"time":1109000,"text":"And that was done with a particle from my shirt."},{"time":1114000,"text":"And the pinhead I've made green around there"},{"time":1118000,"text":"by scraping the particles off a green shirt"},{"time":1121000,"text":"and then pressed onto the needle."},{"time":1123000,"text":"It's very painstaking work,"},{"time":1125000,"text":"but the best things come in small packages."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1128000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1130000,"text":"Bruno Giussani: Willard Wigan!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1132000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}